Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 回贝萨流士家?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总不能一直寄住在兰兹华斯家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给大家添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一点都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都热热闹闹的 很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在我们身边 有些事办起来也会很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 艾米丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真话是不能说出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了嘛 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是回你自己家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好犹豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲? 就是那位说奥兹污秽不堪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么艾丽丝会…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我告诉她的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我还以为自己在很多事情上已经看开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是有点放不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 都过了十年 还这个样子回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你痛苦过的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎伊·贝萨流士公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的成人仪式的夜晚从府邸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur7}向着否定的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲居然已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一直瞒着我到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为难以启齿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安静…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么呢 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我在想前几看到的奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话我大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握了阿嵬茨的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么奥兹大人会有这样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙布利耶的真相 至今仍然未明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 至少知道了阿嵬茨的意志对于杰克·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱有特殊的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊的感情?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小姐的世界是这样解释的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以算是好感的一种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 奥兹被看做是杰克·贝萨流士的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些传闻被阿嵬茨的意志得知了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有必要 重新考虑一下巴斯卡瓦的目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴斯卡瓦的目的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将奥兹看作得到阿嵬茨的意志的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而巴斯卡瓦不是要抓奥兹 却是将他堕入阿嵬茨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说想献出奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来改变阿嵬茨的什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 是想把奥兹大人…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只不过是我的推论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹大人也知道…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看他那样子 其实是很机灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}最后一话让偶发挥下吧= =+果然好可爱啊><
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹少爷!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特夫人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您平安无事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特夫人也很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说老了十岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是奥兹的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐请准备肉类料理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 奥兹少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热腾多汁的肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点不是家吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肮脏的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 在这个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了父亲的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个父亲已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不错的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要住在这个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的父亲生还希望很渺茫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这十年里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想尽了一切办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护贝萨流士家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要尽快让你成为家主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲是和灵体格里风 定下契约之后消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}「格里风」 狮鹫Griffon的音译
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和灵体定下契约了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因和守卫阿嵬茨之门的灵体定下契约 才是四大公爵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯卡叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里风是怎样的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始就一直在你身后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身后?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是把奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堕入阿嵬茨的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事么 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我一个人静静吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然跟巴斯卡瓦穿一条裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 还是他亲手将奥兹 堕入阿嵬茨的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 就连我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实很令人吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HI～～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么出现了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有种不好的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里很乱就过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 奥兹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己关在房间里 不肯出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们只能等了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等下 别擅自插手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手 我等不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是我忍耐的极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我老实点 笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了 海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹是我的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让他任性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来以为他讨厌我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就努力让他喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我的一厢情愿罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就完全否定了我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我逐渐开始明白 父亲给我定的罪究竟是什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我与沙布利耶之悲剧有关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且拥有掌握阿嵬茨一切的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么必须被否定啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奥兹·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么杰克的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的意志跟我没关系!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不正是要去寻找的吗 和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是共同寻找自我的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些只是谎话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算孤身一人我也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法得到别人的认同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能存在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经存在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是早上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎样了呢 你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们担心了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见见那些巴斯卡瓦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 为什么突然间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到了想怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能调查一下他的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据潘多拉的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴斯卡瓦现在的根据地中最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在拉贝优向北约200公里 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙布利耶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是沙布利耶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前的悲剧中被毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原首都沙布利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的想去吗 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仆人可是必须与主人同行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为至今自己所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定都是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如在这里死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是个让人讨厌的顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖出去就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你陪在他身边就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这样 菲利普就很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果除此之外 没有别的方法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会毫不犹豫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样你能满意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说着逃离现实的 一时冲动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不过是个 不谙世事的少爷罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我是个满身缺点的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲的事打击对他不小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎失去自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奥兹谈了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只没用的笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话就别把事推到我身上 自己问去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同感同感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹见了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底打算怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哭一场?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将仇恨和痛苦都宣泄出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想看到那么颓废的奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在父亲的面前亲自…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是想到了复仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了自己的父亲 以泄多年的心头之恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}闭嘴 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭一切障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力向前进发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是非常积极的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 都给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前悲剧的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是个与巴斯卡瓦相称的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了我们会永远和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}说得多好=v=偶的基尔果然最高 / 真基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方说这样的话 真有你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}布雷克说话真不隐晦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打仗的话战友可是必需的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是通往阿嵬茨的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几日你显现的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那位大人下了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然奥兹·贝萨流士 是必须接受制裁的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想见他吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你堕入阿嵬茨的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即刻为你实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,染血黑兔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹靠自己的力量解开了封印!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅一击就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅一击就将贝萨流士公爵的灵体…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹的强大刚才给了我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我又软弱又满是缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不会停止前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在不需要由别人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要由我自己来肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的人怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将不再羞耻 不再迷茫 继续走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以奥兹·贝萨流士的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想来 告诉你这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定一个人 并不是令人愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不能继续存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切也许只是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被谁安排好的 滑稽的童话故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切仍都是谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不会像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一味接受这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想将一切改写为我自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使时间有限…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切谜团被揭开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都结束的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是作者…